text:
Q: Switch Application.Mainform at runtime and invoke MainformOnTaskBar cause flickering on Windows Taskbar A: <p>My working code (Delphi 11, from original source VCL.Forms.pas, You need to call Form.HandleNeeded before change MainForm):</p>
<pre><code>procedure ChangeMainForm([ref] const Form : TForm);
begin

  if Application.MainForm &lt;&gt; Form then
  begin
    Application.MainFormOnTaskBar := False;
    Form.HandleNeeded;
    Pointer((@Application.MainForm)^) := Form;
    Application.MainFormOnTaskBar := true;
  end;

end;
</code></pre>
